snippet.textDisplay:
IMO, France just wanted to secure a draw and preserve their A team, who has already taken enough injuries. The whole team which played the 2/3 of the match were the B team which were far more inferior than our main players. Even the team captain which is our goalkeeper was replaced by the oldest of our players. These are the players Tunisia beat. Also, we saw the French team‚Äôs game increase in the final 20 min with the main players coming onto the pitch, leading to a goal, even though it was controversially refused (the referee didn‚Äôt manage the situation very well).

Well done to Tunisia, but we must take into account they didn‚Äôt play against France‚Äôs Top players.
